<h2 class="bold font-l">Sid translates through Dance</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Manny tries to get the hyraxes to help him steal Gutt's ship, but can't get them to understand him. Sid steps in and uses weird dance moves and making strange sounds to translate the hyraxes. To Manny and Diego's surprise, it works! </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="alt-titles section section-fact">
<h3>
<strong>Alternative Title(s):</strong>
<span>Talks To Squirrels</span>, <span>Fluent In Gibberish</span> </h3>
</div>
